import axios from 'axios'; import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import { Button } from 'react-bootstrap'; import Table from 'react-bootstrap/Table'; const Cow_info = () => { const [reviewCow, setReviewCow] = useState([]); useEffect(() =>{ axios.get('http://localhost:3001/api/cowI').then((response) =>{ setReviewCow(response.data) }) }, []) return (

Limousin Cattle

{reviewCow.map((val)=>{ return (
{/*

ID Number: {val.animalID}

  • SEX: {val.sex}
  • AGE: {val.age}
  • COLOR: {val.color}
  • Father's ID: {val.fathersID}
  • Mother's ID: {val.mothersID}
  • Height: {val.height}
  • Weight: {val.weight}

*/}
# Breed Sex Age Color height Weight Income
{val.animalID} {val.breed} {val.sex} {val.age} {val.color} {val.height} {val.weight} {val.income }
) })}
) } export default Cow_info;
